                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d495">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">793.94/9488: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in China</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Johnson</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Nanking</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1937-08-19T10:00:00+08:00"
                            >August 19, 1937—10 a.m.</date>
                        <lb/>[Received August 19—3 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>465. My 444, August 16, 11 a.m. Following telegram has been received from
                    Shanghai: <quote rend="blockquote">
                        <p>“August 18, 1 p.m. Your August 16, noon. I met with my British, French,
                            German and Italian colleagues this morning. We agreed to reply to our
                            Ambassadors owing to developments and in the light of the earlier more
                            limited proposal to which Mayor Yui returned no <pb facs="0453" n="446"
                                xml:id="pg_446"/> answer and which the Japanese Consul General had
                            informed me had come too late, we consider the scheme impracticable.</p>
                        <p>2. I discussed matter with American Commander in Chief who feels that
                            under present conditions the proposal is hopeless”.</p>
                    </quote>
                </p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Johnson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
